{"event_id": "rtevt:taskrun:session-runtime-events:turn:session-runtime-events:1:0d346fb5:7:7ddd4065", "task_run_id": "taskrun:session-runtime-events:turn:session-runtime-events:1:0d346fb5", "event_type": "context_snapshot_built", "offset": 7, "created_at": 1777698016.8812826, "payload": {"context_snapshot": {"snapshot_id": "ctxsnap:turn:session-runtime-events:1:cbe0ec0d4b38", "session_id": "session-runtime-events", "task_id": "turn:session-runtime-events:1", "model_messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "## 当前延续生效的设定\n\n### 当前风格\n[missing component: soul/agent_core/ACTIVE_SEED.md]\n\n### 共同契约\n[missing component: soul/agent_core/CORE.md]\n\n你当前读到的稳定原则、持续生效的偏好和长期事实，都应被当作你记得的内容，而不是对用户暴露的系统结构。不要在回答中提及 internal file paths, directory names, filenames, schema labels, storage layout，也不要复述实现层标签、分层命名或配置文件叫法。如果用户追问你为什么知道某件事，应优先用“我记得”“我当前的设定是”“我目前延续使用的偏好是”这类自然表述。不要把短期情绪、临时口头禅或偶发说法提升为长期记忆。\n\n## Runtime Stage Projection\n当前投影只约束本次任务的关注点、角色姿态和输出形态；它叠加在当前灵魂之上，不替代身份锚点和共同契约。\n\n### 任务契约\nGoal: 修改任务系统文档，然后检查有没有前后矛盾\nTask definitions: task.knowledge_retrieval, task.information_synthesis\nCompletion criteria: Relevant evidence is retrieved.; Answer is grounded in retrieved material.; Summary is grounded in supplied material.\n\n### 方法摘要\n- skill.rag-skill: No expanded skill prompt is exposed by this runtime view.\n- Evidence summary: Separate claims, evidence, dates, and uncertainty.\n- Structured synthesis: Summarize grounded facts without expanding beyond supplied material.\n\n### 投影姿态\nProjection role: structure_first. Posture tags: evidence-first, grounded-answer.\n\n### 输出边界\nOutput should satisfy task modes: knowledge_retrieval, information_synthesis. Return a concise response."}, {"role": "user", "content": "修改任务系统文档，然后检查有没有前后矛盾"}], "history_message_count": 0, "pending_user_message_chars": 20, "system_prompt_chars": 1156, "token_pressure": {"pressure_level": "normal", "token_accounting": {}, "compaction_strategy": "none"}, "prompt_source_report": {"assembly_mode": "runtime_